export const projects = [

        id: 1,

        id: 3,
        imgLink: "https://github.com/Tgarrey37/super-team-project",

        alt: "Travel Planner Screenshot",
        title: "Travel Planner",
        text: "This application allows the user to search a location to find local weather, hotels, restaurants, and attractions.",

    {
        id: 4,
        imgLink: "https://jacobluedke.github.io/day-planner/",

        github: "https://github.com/jacobluedke/day-planner",
    },
    {
        id: 5,

    },
    {
